      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Combining robust mechanical performance with a well-preserved aesthetic, it exemplifies the standards of excellence our dealership upholds. Every system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure reliability and immediate road-readiness. Experience a sophisticated balance of luxury and utility in a package that commands respect on any road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
